message.content: "Oh, he wasn't. His motor-bike had broken down outside and he noticed your car and then you dancing with this blonde." "Really?" Nigel cocked one eyebrow. "Actually she was brunette at the roots and I had a redhead on the other arm. He would have told you this, too?" "No," she laughed. "He didn't actually see you.
